@node md5 "MD5 message digest algorithm"

MD5 is used for the @{"authentication mechanisms APOP and CRAM-MD5" link cf_network}.

This software contains an MD5 implementation derived from the RSA Data
Security, Inc. MD5 Message-Digest Algorithm.

MD5 is Copyright (C) 1991-2, RSA Data Security, Inc. Created 1991. All
rights reserved.

